    "The value of saving time by improving maintenance processes is often ignored or overlooked (Mobley, 2002).",
    "In situations where delays in repairs could be very expensive, improving maintenance times becomes a priority.",
    "In the aviation industry, devising corrective actions for new maintenance problems is a time sensitive process in a highly stressful environment (Latorella & Prabhu, 2000).",
